Like a curious clown-physicist: marine layer deepened (~2000 ft vs ~1000–1500 yesterday) — MVFR/brief IFR morning, clears mid morning, returns tonight. Afternoon breezy (gusts ~20–25 mph); hazardous seas — SCA until 9 AM. Slight (~10%) coastal drizzle Tuesday. Чую, что скоро развергнутся хляби небесные!